          "name": "Verapamil IV",
          "group": "Antiarrhythmic",
          "critical": false,
          "correct": false,
          "teaching": "⚠️ DANGEROUS in VT — calcium channel blockers cause cardiovascular collapse in ventricular tachycardia. Only appropriate for SVT. If unsure of rhythm, treat as VT.",
