          "group": "Cerebral Edema",
          "critical": true,
          "correct": true,
          "phase": 1,
          "teaching": "Reduces peritumoral vasogenic edema. Rapid clinical improvement expected. This is NOT the same as treating the tumor — it treats the edema around it.",
