      "Hyponatremic encephalopathy (exercise-associated hyponatremia from overhydration — check sodium before giving IV fluids)",
      "Cardiac arrhythmia (hyperthermia + electrolyte derangements + prolonged QTc)",
      "Meningitis/Encephalitis (fever + AMS — consider LP if not improving with cooling)"
