      "Giving antipyretics (acetaminophen, NSAIDs) — these DO NOT work in heat stroke (thermoregulatory failure, not pyrogen-mediated)",
      "Not checking liver function initially and at 48-72 hours — hepatic failure is delayed and can be fatal",
      "Failing to anticipate DIC — serial coagulation studies are mandatory"
